title: Skin Games - The Blood Rush.bin
description:
The Blood Rush by Skin Games. Released 1989. A pop/rock album by an obscure UK band that broke up after this one album release. This is a terrific album with soaring vocals and great pop/rock melodies and thoughtful lyrics. probably somewhat ahead of its time, it doesn&#039;t have a typical "80s sound".

This is a direct binary image of the original CD (Epic Records, catalogue number 01-463285-10) and should be usable by most CD burning software.

I can&#039;t afford to seed this for long so grab it while its hot.
